# Deployment

- Staging: branch `develop` → `docket-staging.baseer.co.uk` / staging API Worker
- Production: tag `v*` → `docket.baseer.co.uk` / `docket-api.humzab1711.workers.dev`
- R2: `docket-documents-staging` / `docket-documents` — never public; presigned URLs only via `lib/r2.ts`
- CORS `APP_URL` must match the live Pages host (`https://docket.baseer.co.uk`)
- Document ops in `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` and `docs/RUNBOOK.md`
